"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The National Rally leader has to decide if she will run with an electronic tag. She will speak on TV later.\",            \"english_title\": \"National Rally Leader Decision\",            \"translated_version\": \"La l\u00edder del Rally Nacional tiene que decidir si correr\u00e1 con un dispositivo electr\u00f3nico. Hablar\u00e1 en la tele m\u00e1s tarde.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Decisi\u00f3n de L\u00edder del Rally Nacional\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Ukrainian president says that decisions for air defense should be a key outcome of this week's summit in Turkey.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukrainian President on Air Defense\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania dice que las decisiones sobre defensa a\u00e9rea deben ser un resultado clave de la cumbre de esta semana en Turqu\u00eda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de Ucrania sobre Defensa A\u00e9rea\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Many people in Ghana were worried that his presence would cause mass protests, so officials say it is postponed for now.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ghana Concerns Over Protests\",            \"translated_version\": \"Muchas personas en Ghana estaban preocupadas de que su presencia causara protestas masivas, as\u00ed que los oficiales dicen que se pospone por ahora.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Preocupaciones en Ghana por Protestas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Videos shared with the BBC show debris flying through the air as a storm hit Ezhou and Huanggang in Hubei province.\",            \"english_title\": \"Storm Hits Hubei Province\",            \"translated_version\": \"Videos compartidos con la BBC muestran escombros volando por el aire cuando una tormenta golpe\u00f3 Ezhou y Huanggang en la provincia de Hubei.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tormenta Golpea Provincia de Hubei\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Police were looking for Anastasiia Berezovska after a Ukrainian millionaire was hurt in a blast.\",            \"english_title\": \"Search for Anastasiia Berezovska\",            \"translated_version\": \"La polic\u00eda buscaba a Anastasiia Berezovska despu\u00e9s de que un millonario ucraniano result\u00f3 herido en una explosi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"B\u00fasqueda de Anastasiia Berezovska\"        }    ]}"